\id JUD - Bunama NT [bdd] -Papua New Guinea 1991 (DBL -2014) 
\h Yude 
\toc1 Yude ꞌina lele 
\toc2 Yude 
\toc3 Yud 
\mt1 YUDE  
\mt2 Yude ꞌina lele  
\ip Yude ꞌina leta bewa ꞌileleya ꞌabehega toheꞌita ꞌaboꞌabo tasanapudi ma taguipailedi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Yauwedo  
\p
\v 1 Taugu Yude, Yesu Keliso ꞌina topaihowa, Yemesa tauna tasigu. Bewa ꞌimi leta yaleleyawa, ꞌomi Tamadai Yehoba ꞌana hesihesinuwao, weyahina ꞌihelauwegomiya ma Yesu Keliso ꞌiꞌitaꞌita yahigomi.  
\v 2 Yehobaina ꞌina ꞌatemuyamuya ta ꞌina yaliyaya ta ꞌina helau ꞌoimiya ꞌihemadou.   
\s1 Toheꞌita ꞌaboꞌabowao  
\p
\v 3 Ciyagwao, nuwanuwagu ma ꞌada ꞌabihetenaina weyahina yaleleyawa, ma hesi geya sawasawahina, weyahina ꞌaigeda mwau ꞌihapwesa pwaiya ꞌoimiya, ꞌoinega ꞌilobwaineya ma leta bewa ꞌoinega yalohatotogomi ma ꞌabehega geyaꞌabwa ꞌida tapwalolo dumwadumwaluna walologwahate, ma hesi wahetapewa weyahina.  
\p Weyahina ꞌida tapwaloloina tauda Yehoba ꞌana tohemisao ꞌiꞌebwae pwaigita.   
\p
\v 4 Mwauina ꞌihapwesa pwaiya ꞌoimiya, beno tupwadi togala siꞌabowegomiya ma ꞌimi boda ꞌoina siluguwa, ꞌoinega Yehoba ꞌina helau ꞌoida taudi ꞌidi heꞌitega sibuiya ma ganawala, ma wete ꞌida Yehoba ma Bada Yesu Keliso silogwahatediya. Taudi ꞌidi galao weyahidi ꞌadi loina mwauna mwalohene Yehoba ꞌina buki ꞌoina silele pwaiya.   
\p
\v 5 Sanapu ꞌaigeda yahegwae hilegomi, weyahina mwalo wanuwa sabwalena, ꞌoinega wada nuwatuhuyahi, beno mwalohene Yehoba ꞌina bodao ꞌiꞌabihetediya eeta sihapwesa tupwa Itipita ꞌoinega, ma muliyetega Yehobaina tupwadi ꞌihunudiya, taudi geya sihemihemisa.   
\p
\v 6 Aneloseyao wete wanuwatuhu yahidi, weyahina mwalo tupwadi taudimo siꞌabi hanehediya, ma ꞌidi ꞌebemiya siꞌebesinediya, ꞌoinega Yehoba ꞌipai momosidiya eeta tupwa guguyou niꞌuwa ꞌoina ꞌilagudiya, ma nobwa ꞌabwa simiyamiya ꞌana siga bwaꞌomatana ꞌana sabwelo ꞌihapwesa.   
\p
\v 7 Taudi ꞌidi mumuga gidemusa tupwadi ꞌasa mwalohene, beno \w Sodoma\w* ma \w Gomola\w* ma tupwadi ꞌasa deidiya, weyahina pui ꞌana nuwaꞌewa madouna ꞌoinega sipaipaihowa besobeso ma ꞌidi ꞌeheloheloheyao mahetediyao sipuipui, ꞌoinega Yehoba ꞌigabudi ꞌaiwe ꞌalaꞌalata hatayana ꞌoina. Ta heꞌitaina bewa mabwaiyada weyahida.   
\p
\v 8 Ma togalaedi silugu pwaiya ꞌoimiya, ꞌidi mumuga mahemahetena, weyahina taudi ꞌidi nihiyao ꞌoidiyega siloina galana, eeta ꞌidi galao ꞌetoi sipaipaihowadi, ꞌaigeda wahidi sigihe bailidi, heluwena toloinao bwebweꞌadi silogwahatediya, ma hetoina tomiya galewa bwebweꞌadi siꞌahwa galagalaedi.  
\v 9 Ma aneloseyao ꞌidi tohanugeta Maikeli mwalohene ꞌiheꞌahupanapanawa Seitani ꞌoina, Mosese wahina weyahina, ma Maikeliina geya Seitani ꞌiꞌasone, ma hesi tuwa ꞌigwaeya, “Bada ꞌiꞌausigo.”   
\p
\v 10 Ma togalaedi, ꞌeguma toꞌaha geya sisanapu, ma tuwa siꞌahwa galagalaedi, weyahina taudi gide hebahebai totopwatula, ta ꞌadi lotohona siloiloinaedi, ma ꞌoinega siboidimo siꞌabiꞌabi hegalaedi.  
\v 11 Nuwaꞌoleꞌoledi weyahina \w Keni\w* ꞌina ꞌeda galana ꞌoinega sitautauya, ma ꞌoinega ꞌidi wasawasa weyahina simumuga galana, gidemusa wete \w Balami\w* mwalo mumugana. Coinega sihesilae, weyahina loina bwebweꞌana silogwahateya, mwalo gidemusa \w Kola\w* tauna loina ꞌilogwahateya.   
\p
\v 12 Ceguma tapwalolo ꞌoina helau ꞌeꞌahaina wapaipaihowa ma ꞌeguma togalaidi siluguwa, ꞌeꞌahaiina siꞌabihegala, weyahina siꞌai hedahedada ma geya sida deba mwadina. Nuwanuwadi taudimo siyaliyaya, ꞌadi ꞌita gide yaloha dubana yaumai ꞌipeineya ma geya dohi. Wete ꞌadi ꞌita gide ꞌaiwe, ꞌina sauga huwa ma geya huwainamo, ꞌoinega sigoha yahule ma ꞌiꞌamasa moisa.  
\v 13 Ma wete ꞌadi ꞌita gide bagodu madoudi ma gwalobusobusodi ꞌidi paihowao ꞌebe deba mwadina. Wete ꞌadi ꞌita gide ꞌipwalao siyawala besobeso galewa, ꞌoinega guguyou ꞌina tupwa simiya hataya.   
\p
\v 14 Mwalohene Inoke togalaedi weyahidi ꞌiloguguya, ma Inokeina ꞌeguma yasoyao tahasilidi Adama ꞌoinega ma ꞌitauya yaso sikisi sigumwala, ma yaso hesebenina beno Inoke ꞌina yaso. Eeta Inokeina ꞌina loguguya ꞌoina ꞌigwaeya,  
\q1 “Waꞌita! Bada ꞌina aneloseyao ꞌasiꞌasilalaidi ma mabwaiyadi mahetenao sinaonaoma,  
\v 15 ma ꞌabehega tomota mabwaiyadi ꞌiloinaedi ma ꞌibwaꞌomatadi, ꞌidi mumuga baibaiwadi ma galadi weyahidi, ma wete ꞌidi ꞌahwa galao mabwaiyana ꞌoina weyahina.”   
\p
\v 16 Tomotaedi tolomugi ma tosinala, ma taudi ꞌadi lotohona ꞌoinega sitautauya. Wete togwaehanehane, ma ꞌeguma ꞌiyadiyao ꞌoidiya sigwae helau, beno tobwatobwa weyahina.   
\s1 Waꞌita yahigomi  
\p
\v 17-18 Ciyagwao, ꞌida Bada Yesu Keliso ꞌana tohepwailao ꞌidi gwae hemisa wanuwatuhuyahi tutaina mwalo sigwaeya, sigwae,  
\q1 “Tuta ꞌana ꞌebelosaloha ꞌoina tupwadi tomota nata mumuga dumwadumwaluna silotuyane, weyahina taudi ꞌadi lotohona galana ꞌiloiloinedi.”   
\p
\v 19 Togalaedi mumuga baleꞌu simulimuliye, ꞌoinega tohekalesiyao ꞌadi towatahao, weyahina Yaluyaluwa Tabuna geya ꞌoidiya.   
\p
\v 20 Ciyagwao, ꞌilobwainegomiya ma tapwalolo dumwaluna waꞌabiyahi momosi ma ꞌoinega wagihe paꞌaligomi, ma wete Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌina waiwaiyega waꞌahwanoi Yehoba ꞌoina,  
\v 21 ma wete helauina Yehoba ꞌoinega waꞌabiyahi, ma wayamwayamwana tolahisa ꞌabwa ꞌida Bada Yesu Keliso ꞌina ꞌatemuyemuyega yawasimi miyamiya hatayana ꞌiꞌebwaegomi.   
\p
\v 22 Ma tupwadi ꞌiyadao geya sihemihemisa moisa, watoho ma wagihenuwa sabwalenidi.  
\v 23 Tupwadi wete ꞌasa ꞌalaꞌalata deina simiyamiya, watoho ma waꞌabihetedi. Tupwadi wete togalagala waꞌatemuyamuyaedi ma walemedi, ma ꞌidi mumuga wamataute, eema mumuga baleꞌu ꞌana tobwatobwao walogwahatedi.   
\s1 Gwae helau  
\p
\v 24 Yehobaina sawasawahina ꞌilomata yahigomi ma geyaꞌabwa wabeꞌubeꞌu ee ꞌana siga tutaina tauna matana ꞌinaolegomi ꞌina ꞌasa ꞌasiꞌasilalaina ꞌoina, maꞌimi mumuga bwebweꞌana, ma wete maꞌimi yaliyaya madouna.  
\v 25 Yehoba taunamo ꞌada Toꞌabihetena. Cabihetenaina ꞌipaihoweya ꞌida Bada Yesu Keliso ꞌina paihowega. Coinega tahepwatuwe ꞌina loina dumwadumwaluna ma waiwaina mwalohene ta nige ma tuta sinaonaoma ꞌoidiya. Emeni.  
\p Taugu Yude.   